Presentation
------------

The SPIP-PMB for Ritimo (spip-pmb4ritimo) GitHub project is a project following 
the evolution of the code of an adaptation/encapsulation of the spip-pmb plugin
for easy deployment in the SPIP websites of members of the Ritimo network.

Ritimo is an information and documentation network on sustainable development
and international aid: http://www.ritimo.org/


